>> title: Hotdogs
>> source: https://www.jamieoliver.com/recipes/eggs-recipes/easy-pancakes/
>> description: A simple recipe for some hotdogs.

Fry a @sausage{1%piece} in a #pan with some @oil{2%tbsp}.

Continue frying for ~{10%min}.

Add @ketchup{to taste} and @mustard{to taste} to an open @bun{1}.

Serve with a @cold drink(1%glass).
